<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5">
    Minor Summoning: Earth</font>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=459"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
    <td valign="top" align="left"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right">
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=459">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=459">
    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell will summon a higher level Earth Elemental. The same rules will apply to the lower level ones except these ones will have higher stats.. It does require a reagent.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>Block of Ore, Words of Tyranny
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
		<table border="1" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td valign="top" align="left">
